IRS990EZ.PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt: TO PROVIDE AN EDUCATION BASED PROGRAM FOR JEWISH YOUNG ADULTS THAT WILL INSTILL STUDENTS WITH A SENSE OF PURPOSE, COMMITMENT AND PRIDE IN THEIR HERITAGE. THIS WILL INCLUDE AN ISRAEL PROGRAM WHICH WILL ALLOW THE STUDENTS TO STRENGTHEN THEIR BOND WITH THEIR RELIGION AND TO GIVE THEM A SENSE OF JEWISH IDENTITY. AND TO SUPPORT OTHER ORGANIZATIONS DEVOTED TO JEWISH EDUCATION, SUPPORT OF TORAH SCHOLARS & NEEDY INDIVIDUALS, AND OTHER JEWISH CAUSES.
